                                <sp
                                    n="1"
                                    xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">
                                    <speaker>Ge.</speaker>
                                    <p>Ex qua tandem corte aut cavea nobis ades?</p>
                                </sp>
                                <sp
                                    n="2"
                                    xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">
                                    <speaker>Li.</speaker>
                                    <p>Quid ita?</p>
                                </sp>
                                <sp
                                    n="3"
                                    xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">
                                    <speaker>Ge.</speaker>
                                    <p>Quia male saginatus. Quia macie pelluces totus, ariditate
                                        crepitas. Unde prodis?</p>
                                </sp>
                            </tei:div>
                        </tei:div>
